{
  "texts": [
    "\"When these classifications are well understood, one can easily embrace the fact that adversarial attacks are quite diverse and complicated and be in a better position to design appropriate protection measures for ML systems against such threats.",
    "In this context, the focus of this work will be on protection against adversarial attacks on the basis of a discussion of relevant research contributions and possible advances.",
    "This study will seek to illustrate ways through which different measures have been utilized in protection against adversarial threats and how further development could be made in relation to the topic at hand with respect to ML.",
    "Thus, our systematic review aims to help advance research in this essential field and inspire innovative approaches.",
    "MethodologyThis study adhered to the methodology used in prior research [60,61] and included a systematic literature review using the preferred reporting items for systematic reviews and meta-analysis (PRISMA) statement."
  ]
}